com.pom.crimson.pages

Class FilteredInterestResultPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BasePage
        • com.pom.crimson.pages.FilteredInterestResultPage

  • public class FilteredInterestResultPage
extends BasePage
    Filtered Interest Result Page articles and videos as per specific interest.
    User can navigate to this page by various ways :

    1. Go to Home Page
    Click Content in bottom menu.
    Click on "Discover by interests" link.
    Click Interest

    2. Go to Home Page
    Click Content in bottom menu.
    Scroll down page and go to "Discover more" section
    Tap on an interest.

    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Jaspreet Kaur Chagger
